{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-diaries-markdown-remark-frontmatter-slug-jsx","path":"/diaries/kashgar-yarkant/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>又一次感受到了时差带给我的新疆震撼，早上八点钟醒了之后整个青旅竟然静悄悄的，搞得我洗漱都要蹑手蹑脚的。可能因为青旅的旅人都是相仿的年纪，有着相同的目的，所以彼此之间意外地好相处，人与人之间的隔阂在此刻变得异常稀薄，一颗葡萄就可以开启一场畅谈，彼此交换旅途中的见闻，甚至可以开启自己的下一段旅程。借我牙膏的兄弟告诉我，他刚从北疆回来，那里旅游业已经乱成一锅粥了，因为暴雪寒潮，禾木、喀纳斯的房价暴涨，随意涨价甚至成了常态，提前预定的一个 looft 三人大通铺，一个地铺要价 600，到了之后还要被临时加价到 800，如果不同意，地铺转手就能以 1000 的价格卖出去。相较于避开的北疆噩梦，显然这次南疆之行堪称完美。</p>\n<p>把衣角卷成一条挂住没有皮带摇摇欲坠的牛仔裤，就这样开始了我的莎车（Yarkant，当地人读音：叶堪 ناھىيىسى，作为一个阿拉伯字母还没认全的人确实拼不出来这个该怎么读）一日游。莎车在喀什的南边，和塔什库尔干隔着公格尔峰和慕士塔格峰，所以在火车上可以远看陪伴了我三天的慕士塔格峰。</p>\n<p>来到莎车要不是路边的双语招牌和随处可见的美团小电车，真的让我有一种来到了异国的错位感。街面上随处可见五官深邃的少数民族同胞，随处可闻自己听不懂的维语腔调，和自己长相一样、语言一样的汉人在这里反而好像是少数。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ad84459cf5995e05945c84af91002bb3/e1596/2023-10-05-yarkant-fruit.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.84662576687117%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"fruit\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/ad84459cf5995e05945c84af91002bb3/6aca1/2023-10-05-yarkant-fruit.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ad84459cf5995e05945c84af91002bb3/d2f63/2023-10-05-yarkant-fruit.jpg 163w,\n/static/ad84459cf5995e05945c84af91002bb3/c989d/2023-10-05-yarkant-fruit.jpg 325w,\n/static/ad84459cf5995e05945c84af91002bb3/6aca1/2023-10-05-yarkant-fruit.jpg 650w,\n/static/ad84459cf5995e05945c84af91002bb3/7c09c/2023-10-05-yarkant-fruit.jpg 975w,\n/static/ad84459cf5995e05945c84af91002bb3/01ab0/2023-10-05-yarkant-fruit.jpg 1300w,\n/static/ad84459cf5995e05945c84af91002bb3/e1596/2023-10-05-yarkant-fruit.jpg 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>得益于美团作为互联网基础设施所带来的便利，在这里随处都可以扫开一辆电瓶车在这座边陲小城中驰骋。存上包跨上车，向着今天的第一站木塔姆餐厅出发。在木塔姆餐厅和来自叶城的维吾尔一家拼桌。男主人是做羊肉养殖的，自己创立了一个羊肉品牌，开设了直播间但是因为转化率低，所以期间非常希望我能够帮他找一个营销主管。吃了顿饭差点变成猎头也是神奇。不过也让我感受到了这个地方的人对于发展、对于赚钱的渴望和迫切。这可能和这十几年新疆发生的天翻地覆的变化有关。莎车县城面貌像极了十几年前洛阳的样子，但是她的内在还停留在更远之前。尽管在中心城区已经发展起了繁荣的小商贸，盖起了不大不小的贸易商厦，路上尽是匆匆忙忙赶路的市民。但是在老城区的边缘还存在着过去的痕迹，脏兮兮的孩子三三两两的扎堆儿，其中甚至总能看到一个打赤板的。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/33f7612ef7f534b25d355e3791122b7f/e1596/2023-10-05-yarkant-old-city.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.84662576687117%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"old city\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/33f7612ef7f534b25d355e3791122b7f/6aca1/2023-10-05-yarkant-old-city.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/33f7612ef7f534b25d355e3791122b7f/d2f63/2023-10-05-yarkant-old-city.jpg 163w,\n/static/33f7612ef7f534b25d355e3791122b7f/c989d/2023-10-05-yarkant-old-city.jpg 325w,\n/static/33f7612ef7f534b25d355e3791122b7f/6aca1/2023-10-05-yarkant-old-city.jpg 650w,\n/static/33f7612ef7f534b25d355e3791122b7f/7c09c/2023-10-05-yarkant-old-city.jpg 975w,\n/static/33f7612ef7f534b25d355e3791122b7f/01ab0/2023-10-05-yarkant-old-city.jpg 1300w,\n/static/33f7612ef7f534b25d355e3791122b7f/e1596/2023-10-05-yarkant-old-city.jpg 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bb8d01e035a02133a7ee47c3fee0f638/ac99c/2023-10-05-yarkant-door.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.12883435582822%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"old door\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/bb8d01e035a02133a7ee47c3fee0f638/6aca1/2023-10-05-yarkant-door.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bb8d01e035a02133a7ee47c3fee0f638/d2f63/2023-10-05-yarkant-door.jpg 163w,\n/static/bb8d01e035a02133a7ee47c3fee0f638/c989d/2023-10-05-yarkant-door.jpg 325w,\n/static/bb8d01e035a02133a7ee47c3fee0f638/6aca1/2023-10-05-yarkant-door.jpg 650w,\n/static/bb8d01e035a02133a7ee47c3fee0f638/7c09c/2023-10-05-yarkant-door.jpg 975w,\n/static/bb8d01e035a02133a7ee47c3fee0f638/01ab0/2023-10-05-yarkant-door.jpg 1300w,\n/static/bb8d01e035a02133a7ee47c3fee0f638/ac99c/2023-10-05-yarkant-door.jpg 1536w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>骑着小电车在老城的各个巷子里穿行，几分钟便可以遇到一个古迹遗址，比如玄奘讲经台、伊斯兰古寺。当然最能吸引我的还是当地居民装饰精美的大门和顽皮和天真的孩子们。在去讲经台的路上偶遇一群叽叽喳喳的小男生，像极了我小时候和朋友们啸聚山林时的模样。他们用着维语特有的语调对着我的背影大喊“摩托！摩托！”出于好奇我倒回去问他们刚刚在说什么，结果领头的那个以为我要找他们麻烦，竟然后退了一步。在确认了我是个人畜无害的大白兔之后，他们竟然打起了我的电瓶车的主意。围着我喊着什么“rishi！rishi！rishi 摩托”还怕我听不懂“黄色的摩托”“让我们骑摩托”。出于保护祖国未来花骨朵的初衷和不想体验被他们抢了“rishi 摩托”的窘态，我果断拒绝了他们，只留下一串大笑回荡在小巷子里。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/be766962a9b5e386f624c71737a7f90c/ac99c/2023-10-05-yarkant-and-internet.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.12883435582822%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"yarkant internet\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/be766962a9b5e386f624c71737a7f90c/6aca1/2023-10-05-yarkant-and-internet.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/be766962a9b5e386f624c71737a7f90c/d2f63/2023-10-05-yarkant-and-internet.jpg 163w,\n/static/be766962a9b5e386f624c71737a7f90c/c989d/2023-10-05-yarkant-and-internet.jpg 325w,\n/static/be766962a9b5e386f624c71737a7f90c/6aca1/2023-10-05-yarkant-and-internet.jpg 650w,\n/static/be766962a9b5e386f624c71737a7f90c/7c09c/2023-10-05-yarkant-and-internet.jpg 975w,\n/static/be766962a9b5e386f624c71737a7f90c/01ab0/2023-10-05-yarkant-and-internet.jpg 1300w,\n/static/be766962a9b5e386f624c71737a7f90c/ac99c/2023-10-05-yarkant-and-internet.jpg 1536w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>摆脱了未来的鬼火少年之后，又遇上了三个莎车小天使，在我自拍的时候懂事地停在一边等我忙完，擦肩时还主动打招呼“你好”。最后很巧的是我绕了一圈之后，在一个十字路口又一次和她们相遇了，这次我换主动邀请和她们合照，她们也欣然接受了。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0671fa980dc0708293bf9e71bc37acfd/a7895/2023-10-05-yarkant-little-angel.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 94.47852760736197%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"little angel\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/0671fa980dc0708293bf9e71bc37acfd/6aca1/2023-10-05-yarkant-little-angel.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0671fa980dc0708293bf9e71bc37acfd/d2f63/2023-10-05-yarkant-little-angel.jpg 163w,\n/static/0671fa980dc0708293bf9e71bc37acfd/c989d/2023-10-05-yarkant-little-angel.jpg 325w,\n/static/0671fa980dc0708293bf9e71bc37acfd/6aca1/2023-10-05-yarkant-little-angel.jpg 650w,\n/static/0671fa980dc0708293bf9e71bc37acfd/7c09c/2023-10-05-yarkant-little-angel.jpg 975w,\n/static/0671fa980dc0708293bf9e71bc37acfd/01ab0/2023-10-05-yarkant-little-angel.jpg 1300w,\n/static/0671fa980dc0708293bf9e71bc37acfd/a7895/2023-10-05-yarkant-little-angel.jpg 1826w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>最后骑到老城边缘，停了车子准备徒步前往下一处遗址。结果遇到了两个主动搭讪的小女孩，一红一白好似两个怀揣着恶作剧心思的小恶魔。她们主动给我带路，有一搭没一搭地跨服聊天。直到她俩看着拐弯处鬼鬼祟祟的小鬼头憋笑，我就知道这群小屁孩估计是想拿我这个孤身旅人开涮。我停下来把埋伏着的小绿林好汉一起喊出来聊天，结果他们自己作鸟兽散了。也就没有机会了，因为孩子们说不愿意拍照，所以也就没有留下来照片，但是她们的一句话让我触动挺大的“上海好玩么？我没出去过”。</p>\n<p>叶尔羌王陵对我而言就是一个收费的木塔姆博物馆，无甚抢眼之处，但是莎车的孩子们却深深地刻印在了我的脑子里。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e588e3e0cb82505aec942cf700292239/ac99c/2023-10-05-yarkant-museum.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.12883435582822%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"yarkant museum\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/e588e3e0cb82505aec942cf700292239/6aca1/2023-10-05-yarkant-museum.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e588e3e0cb82505aec942cf700292239/d2f63/2023-10-05-yarkant-museum.jpg 163w,\n/static/e588e3e0cb82505aec942cf700292239/c989d/2023-10-05-yarkant-museum.jpg 325w,\n/static/e588e3e0cb82505aec942cf700292239/6aca1/2023-10-05-yarkant-museum.jpg 650w,\n/static/e588e3e0cb82505aec942cf700292239/7c09c/2023-10-05-yarkant-museum.jpg 975w,\n/static/e588e3e0cb82505aec942cf700292239/01ab0/2023-10-05-yarkant-museum.jpg 1300w,\n/static/e588e3e0cb82505aec942cf700292239/ac99c/2023-10-05-yarkant-museum.jpg 1536w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>不虚此行，就用莎车站九点的夜景作为今天的收尾吧。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/afa45abd8216021982043188221db571/e1596/2023-10-05-yarkant-station.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.84662576687117%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"yarkant station\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/afa45abd8216021982043188221db571/6aca1/2023-10-05-yarkant-station.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/afa45abd8216021982043188221db571/d2f63/2023-10-05-yarkant-station.jpg 163w,\n/static/afa45abd8216021982043188221db571/c989d/2023-10-05-yarkant-station.jpg 325w,\n/static/afa45abd8216021982043188221db571/6aca1/2023-10-05-yarkant-station.jpg 650w,\n/static/afa45abd8216021982043188221db571/7c09c/2023-10-05-yarkant-station.jpg 975w,\n/static/afa45abd8216021982043188221db571/01ab0/2023-10-05-yarkant-station.jpg 1300w,\n/static/afa45abd8216021982043188221db571/e1596/2023-10-05-yarkant-station.jpg 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>回到喀什打车的时候又一次遇到了司机不打表按人头收费的情况，因为我上午打车去车站知道打表大概要 15，所以我一口咬死了这个价格，但是同车的两个小情侣不一样啊，特么的差不多近的地方被这个“阿达西”要了 30，我特么听到他们付款时的对话我整个人都傻了。虽然我和这位维族阿达西聊的很嗨就是了，罪过罪过。</p>\n<p>“喀什，有意思的是人”。</p>\n<p>明天，喀什古城西半边，喀什博物馆和五十六朵花缸子肉！</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"October 05, 2023","slug":"/kashgar-yarkant","title":"莎车一日游"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"4b89c74a-e85f-5df9-ab87-4f87e3f18a9f","frontmatter__slug":"/kashgar-yarkant","__params":{"frontmatter__slug":"kashgar-yarkant"}}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}